The shipped `ecdict.db` is a *starter* English‚ÜíChinese dictionary (~88
hand-picked picture-book words). It is original content under the same
MIT license as this project.

To replace it with the full ECDICT lite (~110 000 entries):

1. Download `ecdict.csv` from https://github.com/skywind3000/ECDICT
   (MIT license, mirror anywhere offline-friendly).
2. From the project root:

       dart run tool/build_dict.dart path/to/ecdict.csv

3. Commit the resulting `assets/dict/ecdict.db`.

Either way the .db is committed; the app NEVER fetches it at runtime.

ECDICT itself: https://github.com/skywind3000/ECDICT ‚Äî MIT License.
